{"tid":664504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川航空一航班飛空途中機頭整塊玻璃粉碎，駕駛艙部份組件被扯走","createTime":"2018-05-14T06:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T12:07:46.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"122d45e8fcf8bf767ec39d226a807fbc5ca91e35","tid":664504,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DdH1Z_6U8AAYa5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDdH1Z_6U8AAYa5g.jpg&h=a887e88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DdH1cfmVAAAlHGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDdH1cfmVAAAlHGB.jpg&h=3955b692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n初初以為只係爆，無粉碎，點知原來係碎晒，半組FCU唔見左<br />\n<br />\nSichuan 3U8633 from Chongqing to Lhasa diverted to Chengdu. Lost one windshield at FL332. Descend to FL240 due to high terrain (@flightradar24 data). Cabin decomp. FCU failure and some parts sucked out. Landded safely with bust tires. One pilot and one cabin crew injured.<br />\n<br />\nWe have more detail from the airline: inside layer of right windshield cracked at FL331. Crew started divert to Chengdu. ECAM showing right windshield anti-ice error. Then entire windshield cracked and lost."},{"pid":"cf5028deae5fbac2d7f3d64a1e558d2c7cea6b37","tid":664504,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3U8633-Flight-Path-and-Graph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flightradar24.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F3U8633-Flight-Path-and-Graph.jpg&h=da3af0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好好彩係剛剛飛入四川高原先爆，可以即刻divert去CTU，飛到半路都唔知繼續飛LXA定去CTU好"},{"pid":"3d8cab7aec324c640917c2ca8d3380bde5419a5b","tid":664504,"uid":44560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf5028deae5